    • apply

      public WebEngineBuilder apply(Consumer<WebEngine> func)
      Applies a function to the WebEngine instance currently being built. Most operations on the instance can be performed using this method.

      Example usage:

      
 apply(webEngine -> webEngine.setId("Main" + webEngine.getTypeSelector()))
      Returns:
      builder instance
